-childs-independent-women-part-i-3247082">凯莉·罗兰</a>(Kelly Rowland)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-stereophonics-kelly-jones-join-coldplay-on-stage-at-cardiff-gig-footage-setlist-3452463">Stereophonics 的凯莉·琼斯 (Kelly Jones</a> ) 等特邀嘉宾给观众带来惊喜</p><p>《Music Of The Spheres》是酷玩乐队最后一张正式发行的专辑，尽管乐队去年确实分享了独立单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-share-new-biutyful-video-featuring-alien-band-the-weirdos-3263256">《Biutyful》</a> 。就戈麦斯而言，她在八月发行了她最新的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-shares-empowering-new-track-single-soon-3488569">“Single Soon”</a> ，并在尚未发行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a>曲目的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fred-again-preview-new-song-featuring-selena-gomez-3485807">预览中亮相</a>。 HER 的最新单曲“The Journey”于五月发布。</p><p> <i>NME</i>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/coldplay-music-of-the-spheres-review-3070711">《Music Of The Spheres》的四星评论</a>中写道：“这张专辑充满了高亢的流行旋律，让你进入足够高的轨道，感人的情感让你周围的宇宙变得更加明亮。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-selena-gomez-h-e-r-live-rendition-let-somebody-go-3508176">观看 Coldplay、赛琳娜·戈麦斯 (Selena Gomez) 和 HER 现场表演“Let Somebody Go”后，</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首先出现。</p> ;
